  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK465">
<l>vakaiyaṟac cūḻā teḻutal pakaivaraip</l>
<l>pāttip paṭuppatō rāṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>One way to promote the prosperity of an enemy, is (for a king) to set out (to war) without having thoroughly weighed his ability (to cope with its chances).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
